     当<varname>DateStyle</>参数被设置为非<literal>ISO</>输出时，<literal>postgres_verbose</>风格的输出匹配<productname>PostgreSQL</> 8.4版本以前的输出。
    </para>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
    <para>
     The output of the <literal>iso_8601</> style matches the <quote>format
     with designators</> described in section 4.4.3.2 of the
     ISO 8601 standard.
    </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
